% ============================================================================
% pccx — BibTeX reference database
%
% Shared between the English (root conf.py) and Korean (ko/conf.py) builds.
% Cite in prose via MyST:   {cite}`key`
% Or via RST:               :cite:`key`
%
% Render a bibliography section at the end of a page by adding a bibliography
% directive with filter "docname in docnames".
%
% Naming convention: {firstauthor_lowercase}{year}_{topic}
%   e.g. gemma3n_2024_overview, dsp48e2_w4a8_2023_derivation
%
% NOTE: pybtex keys off a leading at-sign regardless of a preceding %, and will
% try to parse commented-out template entries as real ones — so DO NOT keep
% scaffolded entries here. Start a new entry fresh; template lives in CLAUDE.md
% section 8.5.
% ============================================================================
